<br>
Ok, I've noticed this phenomenon with Tishans Discord, it appears to be a &quot;bug&quot;, since on the same mobs it actually stunned them, and other times it did not, there have been no notes made that indicate that the stun factor is 0-5 sec, it's simply supposed to be 5 secs., don't get rid of Markers just yet! =p<br>
